      "text": {
        "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Problem\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Problem</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Solution\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Solution</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Solution_2_.28credit_to_dskull16.29\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Solution 2 (credit to dskull16)</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#See_Also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See Also</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Problem\">Problem</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Problem\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Let <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/5/b/a5b29b358e825defa3e11b7d903d43ec31e5909a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a,b,c$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"43\" height=\"18\" /> be positive real numbers such that <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/e/3/2e32cfd3a6f5f31f73d0b272a5f7b1638fd16551.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$abc = 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"57\" height=\"13\" />. Prove that:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/c/f/2cffcabdd9b8890107e7ea6c919339a85bb607ce.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\prod(a^5+a^4+a^3+a^2+a+1)\\geq 8(a^2+a+1)(b^2+b+1)(c^2+c+1).$\" style=\"vertical-align: -8px\" width=\"547\" height=\"25\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution\">Solution</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Solution\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Since <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/2/e/3/2e32cfd3a6f5f31f73d0b272a5f7b1638fd16551.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$abc = 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"57\" height=\"13\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/d/5/5d54af1ccae66874802051ed7643065e8c6718b8.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a = \\tfrac{1}{bc}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -6px\" width=\"48\" height=\"21\" />. By <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/AM-GM_Inequality\" title=\"AM-GM Inequality\">AM-GM Inequality</a>,\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/f/4/ef4ac500c2909b09f55ba14a3e428c792b0461e4.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} b^3c^3 + \\frac{1}{b^3c^3} &amp;\\ge 2 \\\\ b^3 + \\frac{1}{b^3} &amp;\\ge 2 \\\\ c^3 + \\frac{1}{c^3} &amp;\\ge 2. \\end{align*}\" width=\"123\" height=\"123\" />\nAdding the inequalities together and factoring yields\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/0/0/d0055102e55ad96e537884c0c8678e387f3c3f90.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} 1 + c^3 + \\frac{1}{c^3} + 1 + b^3 + b^3c^3 + \\frac{1}{b^3c^3} + \\frac{1}{b^3} &amp;\\ge 8 \\\\ (1+c^3)(1 + \\frac{1}{c^3} + b^3 + \\frac{1}{b^3c^3}) &amp;\\ge 8 \\\\ (1+c^3)(1+b^3)(1 + \\frac{1}{b^3c^3}) &amp;\\ge 8 \\\\ (1+c^3)(1+b^3)(1 + a^3) &amp;\\ge 8. \\end{align*}\" width=\"343\" height=\"149\" />\nSince <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/5/b/a5b29b358e825defa3e11b7d903d43ec31e5909a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a,b,c$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"43\" height=\"18\" /> are positive, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/4/8/e/48efd1c3040707e07903e0b6e011cbb6e1d59283.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^2 + a + 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"79\" height=\"16\" />, <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/4/e/a4e0acf01e5a01efed7d15614cad0b942ff67aaf.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$b^2 + b + 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -2px\" width=\"78\" height=\"18\" />, and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/0/1/3/013d84c1cdff2fbb8f0449446d34669c0f885bd5.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$c^2 + c + 1$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"75\" height=\"16\" /> are all greater than 0.  That means\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/e/8/1/e814dccb6126295d2673f0ca2c77158b99005a7f.png\" class=\"latexcenter\" alt=\"\\begin{align*} \\prod(a^3 + 1)(a^2 + a + 1) &amp;\\ge 8(a^2+a+1)(b^2+b+1)(c^2+c+1) \\\\ \\prod \\left( (a^3 + 1)\\frac{a^3 - 1}{a-1} \\right) &amp;\\ge 8(a^2+a+1)(b^2+b+1)(c^2+c+1) \\\\ \\prod \\frac{a^6 -1}{a-1} &amp;\\ge 8(a^2+a+1)(b^2+b+1)(c^2+c+1) \\\\ \\prod(a^5+a^4+a^3+a^2+a+1) &amp;\\ge 8(a^2+a+1)(b^2+b+1)(c^2+c+1). \\end{align*}\" width=\"547\" height=\"156\" />\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Solution_2_(credit_to_dskull16)\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Solution_2_.28credit_to_dskull16.29\">Solution 2 (credit to dskull16)</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Solution 2 (credit to dskull16)\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Note that the inequality clearly holds when <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/9/7/c/97ca632aa29bb33ff08eae40399f5bed63a2bd0f.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a=b=c=1$\" style=\"vertical-align: 0px\" width=\"106\" height=\"13\" /> and the method below can be used to verify the inequality is true in the case where one of <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/5/b/a5b29b358e825defa3e11b7d903d43ec31e5909a.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a,b,c$\" style=\"vertical-align: -4px\" width=\"43\" height=\"18\" /> is one (to avoid complications with dividing by zero).\n</p><p>Write <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/c/8/b/c8bbc9a5663223f46dd6381c80f6785f3e31fc24.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^5+a^4+a^3+a^2+a+1 = \\frac{a^6-1}{a-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"276\" height=\"42\" />\n</p><p>Write <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/7/e/a/7eae3740a8001d579d6c6a2601cd1478a2a1d650.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^2 + a + 1 = \\frac{a^3-1}{a-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"159\" height=\"42\" /> by the sum of a geometric series formula. Thus we get:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/d/7/5/d759d77597464f3e1039b253d31026f751e9cc33.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\frac{a^6-1}{a-1}\\cdot\\frac{b^6-1}{b-1}\\cdot\\frac{c^6-1}{c-1} \\geq 8\\cdot\\frac{a^3-1}{a-1}\\cdot\\frac{b^3-1}{b-1}\\cdot\\frac{c^3-1}{c-1}$\" style=\"vertical-align: -15px\" width=\"408\" height=\"42\" />\n</p><p>Multiply both sides by <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/7/6/4/764c3921c3c1159b74e0fbe8d1f7c5d38432f683.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(a-1)(b-1)(c-1)$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"163\" height=\"20\" /> and recognise the difference of two squares to get:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/5/5/d/55dd1ec28cb0849af1d7bb7f84e3a8ffbff6be76.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(a^3+1)(b^3+1)(c^3+1) \\geq 8$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"219\" height=\"21\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/b/1/8/b1836aacbefbeee9c1a1f7747dd94c2a3378c4b0.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies (abc)^3 + a^3 + b^3 + c^3 + (ab)^3 + (bc)^3 + (ac)^3 + 1 \\geq 8$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"454\" height=\"21\" />\n<img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/b/b/3/bb369f74743c45ec0f51dd101b44671855a1ccce.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$\\implies a^3 + b^3 + c^3 + (ab)^3 + (bc)^3 + (ac)^3 \\geq 6$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"354\" height=\"21\" />\n</p><p>Now use AM-GM on each of <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/9/a/7/9a70858379029b66b2607e3f0fccbd8c76f1d648.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^3 + b^3 + c^3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -1px\" width=\"91\" height=\"16\" /> and <img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/7/b/a/7ba6429a334f33cc3384334945defaa7d66ee701.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(ab)^3 + (bc)^3 + (ac)^3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"162\" height=\"21\" /> to obtain:\n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/6/1/a/61ab413cf8a185a8abd7f768ebcf661c3cdffa1b.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$a^3 + b^3 + c^3 \\geq 3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -3px\" width=\"127\" height=\"19\" /> \n</p><p><img src=\"//latex.artofproblemsolving.com/a/8/7/a87da38c2d09813f60304abbde6c54cad0e752ce.png\" class=\"latex\" alt=\"$(ab)^3 + (bc)^3 + (ac)^3 \\geq 3$\" style=\"vertical-align: -5px\" width=\"195\" height=\"21\" />\n</p><p>which combines to give the final result.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_Also\">See Also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/wiki/index.php?title=2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_1&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: See Also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:95%; border:1px solid black; width:80%;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"background:#ccf;text-align:center;\" colspan=\"3\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2011_JBMO\" title=\"2011 JBMO\">2011 JBMO</a></b> (<b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2011_JBMO_Problems\" title=\"2011 JBMO Problems\">Problems</a></b> • <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://artofproblemsolving.com/community/c13_contests\">Resources</a>)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"50%\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\">Preceded&#160;by<br /><b>First Problem</b>\n</td>\n<td width=\"50%\" align=\"center\" rowspan=\"1\">Followed&#160;by<br /><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_2\" title=\"2011 JBMO Problems/Problem 2\">Problem 2</a></b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">1</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_2\" title=\"2011 JBMO Problems/Problem 2\">2</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_3\" title=\"2011 JBMO Problems/Problem 3\">3</a> <b>•</b> <a href=\"/wiki/index.php/2011_JBMO_Problems/Problem_4\" title=\"2011 JBMO Problems/Problem 4\">4</a> <b></b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><b><a href=\"/wiki/index.php/JBMO_Problems_and_Solutions,_with_authors\" title=\"JBMO Problems and Solutions, with authors\"> All JBMO Problems and Solutions</a></b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240907090002\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.039 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.056 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 265/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 699/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 839/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 43/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 5535/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   13.482      1 Template:JBMO_box\n100.00%   13.482      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki-wiki_:pcache:idhash:16758-0!canonical and timestamp 20240907090002 and revision id 216436\n -->\n"
